    "## 11. Skill Gap Analysis\n",
    "\n",
    "Recommending a career is only half the job. The other half is telling the person what\n",
    "they need to work on to actually get there. That is what Skill Gap Analysis does.\n",
    "\n",
    "For each feature we compare the user's current score against the score required by\n",
    "their top recommended occupation. A positive gap means the user already meets or\n",
    "exceeds the requirement. A negative gap is an area that needs development.\n",
    "\n",
    "We then classify each gap into three priority levels: HIGH urgency means the gap\n",
    "is large and this trait is critical for the occupation. MEDIUM means a noticeable\n",
    "gap that is worth addressing. LOW means a small gap that is unlikely to be a\n",
    "barrier in practice."
   ]
  },
